ing: 4 ounces BelGioioso Fresh Mozzarella cheese, sliced
des: "This roasted vegetable panini with fresh mozzarella cheese and prosciuto is cut into bite-size pieces--a great way to use leftover grilled veggies!"
ins: Place all ingredients between the two pieces of bread and press while grilling to create a delicious panini sandwich. Cut into bite-size servings.
